## 3. 🎨 USABILITY & PREMIUM DESIGN
*Objective: Evaluate visual excellence and accessibility.*

### 3.1: Visual Excellence (Rich Aesthetics)
- [ ] **Glassmorphism:** Uses backdrop-blur and translucent backgrounds (`bg-gray-50/50`).
- [ ] **Modern Typography:** Uses Inter/Outfit; readable line height (1.5+).
- [ ] **Grid/Layout:** Clean 2-column layout on Desktop; responsive stack on Mobile.
- [ ] **Micro-animations:** Smooth Fade-in/Slide-up on tool entry.

### 3.2: Mobile Usability
- [ ] **Touch Targets:** Buttons are at least 44x44px.
- [ ] **Responsive Output:** Results box is scrollable and doesn't break page width.
- [ ] **Input Focus:** Keyboard doesn't hide the "Analyze" button on smaller screens.

### 3.3: Accessibility (a11y)
- [ ] **Tab Order:** Logical flow from input -> action -> output.
- [ ] **Aria-Labels:** Used on icon buttons (Copy, Download).
- [ ] **Color Contrast:** High enough for light/dark modes (WCAG AA).

